Reiner returned after an hour, clad in his well fitted black leather armor with his twin blade on both sides of his hips. The armor was adorned by smaller throwing knives. He puled another garment a robe and put it over his armor. He then stared at his companions looking for signs of readiness. When he was satisfied he said, &quot; It's time, we have to go to the gnome city first through the area unhibaited by demons from there we go to the elves. That way we have lesser encounter with them.&quot;<br>
