Reine started to wlak outside the barracks motioning for the others to come with him. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showMessageRange?topicID=2.topic&start=81&stop=92>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showPrevMessage?topicID=2.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.showNextMessage?topicID=2.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.emailToFriend?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.threadControl?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/deleteThreadFire.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fgoergyboysroleplayingpalacefrm12.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/them